WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:02.333
Ok, I know you're sad too.

2
00:00:02.333 --> 00:00:03.200
I miss my grandfather

3
00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.300
But ah, you have to pay attention to your body.

4
00:00:05.300 --> 00:00:06.400
What about after these three days?

5
00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:08.700
Let's hold a funeral for the old man

6
00:00:08.700 --> 00:00:09.400
What then?

7
00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:10.400
What about the Chens?

8
00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.100
Will come from all over

9
00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:13.966
Send the old man the last ride

10
00:00:13.966 --> 00:00:14.933
After 7 days?

11
00:00:14.933 --> 00:00:17.200
Our family friend

12
00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:20.733
The rich and powerful in Kyoto will come to worship

13
00:00:20.733 --> 00:00:22.000
Will you be busy then?

14
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.166
Please don't get sick

15
00:00:24.166 --> 00:00:26.700
Yeah, and the blood, you came all the way here

16
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:27.366
Also tired

17
00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:30.066
I'll ask Auntie to make some food for you when it rains on ice cubes

18
00:00:30.066 --> 00:00:32.800
How about you also persuade Xiaodou not to make him too sad?

19
00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:37.600
The person who killed grandpa

20
00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:40.233
I won't let him go no matter who he is

21
00:00:54.066 --> 00:00:56.400
It's all me, just you

